<p></p><h3>The 4th ASFAA Sport for All Training Course will be held in Macau, China. </h3><p>The theme of this year is “Sports for All and Quality of Life of Citizens” – The course is designed to provide a structural and practical training to personnel involved or about to engage in the field of Sport for All. Participants that successfully complete the course will receive a certificate from ASFAA. Participants are required to have a good command of English as this is the official course language. Simultaneous translation in English and Mandarin will be available in all training sessions.</p><p>For more details, please check the dedicated website at:</p><p><a href="http://sport.gov.mo/en/calendary/type/item/id/6334">http://sport.gov.mo/en/calendary/type/item/id/6334</a></p><p></p>